# Week 4 

In our meeting with Kim, he minstioned how could the info window be represnted. The most important think with the info window is to make the language as simple as possible,
use "Lätt svenska" so any user could benifet from this web-application. He suggested to make the markers change its colour depending on the availability of the parking.


