# Week 5 

This week me and Anas continued working on map and improving the pop-up info window, we added relevant info that we
think is the most important for the user. 
We had an issue whith the database, where there is a location that has no number of spaces, and this caused the application to crach when getting the number
of spaces for all parkings. We fixed it by adding a condition to show "Ej tillänglig" when this data is missing. We presented this issue with the database in our meeting with Kim.  

In our meeting with Kim, Jonas och Lisa they suggested that adding a highlaigth/border araound the area when the user search up for a parking with multiple postions.
This would give the user a better experience and make it easier to know exactly where a specific parking is located. We are thinking to add this feature in the following sprint next week. 

